WEBVTT

00:08:59.364 --> 00:09:00.864
every single day.

00:09:02.212 --> 00:09:06.305
Listening to her, I felt
this familiar panic rise in me,

00:09:06.948 --> 00:09:09.386
the residue of my own childhood.

00:09:10.441 --> 00:09:12.035
When I was 10 years old,

00:09:12.059 --> 00:09:14.633
my father lay on the living room floor

00:09:14.657 --> 00:09:17.768
in the grips of one
of his many depressions.

00:09:18.435 --> 00:09:22.348
As I crouched next to him, he told me
that he wanted to kill himself.

00:09:25.721 --> 00:09:27.804
My father lived,

00:09:27.828 --> 00:09:29.378
but he struggled to work.

00:09:29.939 --> 00:09:31.532
And my family survived,